{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":9,"day":4}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"将军，不能这样做","authors":["叶文福"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史，总是艰难地解答一个又一个新的课题而前进的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说，一位遭“四人帮”残酷迫害的高级将领，重新走上领导岗位后，竟下令拆掉幼儿园，为自己盖楼房；全部现代化设备，耗用了几十万元外汇。我……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怎么说……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是受人尊敬的前辈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是后之来者。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你我之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着硝烟弥漫的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十年代、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十年代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批评你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有想过。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许正是你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用抱着机关枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向旧世界猛烈扫射"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把抽在我脊梁上的皮鞭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把夺过——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把我搂在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满是血污"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和热汗的胸前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大滴的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砰然而落！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你抽泣着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚摸我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身的伤疤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厚厚的嘴唇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哆嗦着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了——”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我赤着脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小的脚丫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩着你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又深又大的脚窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走进了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不！将军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使是这样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也要说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我更应该说！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记得么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢渡泸定桥——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后：追兵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对岸：烈火！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一河如虎的浪山呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几根沉沉铁索……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在危崖上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦灼——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道井冈山的火种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要被这大渡河水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无情吞没？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你大瞪着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布满血丝的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驳壳枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往腰间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛地一掖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声呼啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似万钧雷霆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挟带着雄风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲进了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的史册！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你想的什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我敢说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你想的是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“为子孙后代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都过上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福的生活！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说的是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“最艰巨的任务"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给我！……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么不幸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的浑身弹痕的将军呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四十多年后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你英雄的身躯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟会让功劳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步履蹒跚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你雷霆般的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被时光的流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵蚀得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么孱弱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“给我……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“给我……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给你月亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你嫌太冷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给你太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你嫌太热！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你想把地球"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搂在怀里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都供你欣赏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你选择……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么都要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你什么都要！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是不要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你入党时的誓言？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是不要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级的本色？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道大渡河水都无法吞没的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山火种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟要熄灭在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茅台酒杯之中？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道能让南湖风雨中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰来的红船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你的安乐椅上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搁浅、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"停泊？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道一个共产党人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟要去写"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛金星们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可悲的历史？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道一代一代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭竿而起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殊死抗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟只是为了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你一家人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无止无休地享乐？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果真的是这样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怎么对得起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牺牲在你怀里的战友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后的嘱托？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么对得起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那白发苍苍的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《共产党宣言》的作者？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去呵，将军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿上当年的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红缨草鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去吻吻你曾为之流血的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吧——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一寸一寸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从敌人手中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺过来的土地呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一寸一寸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从苦难深渊中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捞起来的土地呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一寸一寸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打着革命印记的土地呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一寸一寸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养育过红军、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八路军、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新四军、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放军的土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喂过你小米汤的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那太行母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手中的木勺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在碗里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搅拌着野菜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年为你包扎伤口的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洛阳大嫂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一家三代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堆在一间六平方米的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小屋子里："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"床上架锅……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的官高权重的将军呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你戎马征战几十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到底为的什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"置人民疾苦于不顾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个共产党员的良心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道就不受"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理的谴责？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫非你真的坚信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"法律"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远是你手中的纸牌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者至多是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏夜柔和的晚风？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身的毛孔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在竟渗不进一丁点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周总理的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美德？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了你的“现代化”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼儿园都拆掉了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后人都不管了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满头飞雪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你还能舒适几年？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天是孩子们的、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是孩子们的呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子们都不要了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁来捧你的骨灰盒？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你骄傲地说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我有儿子……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，你有儿子——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的儿子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他就会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愤而离开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的高楼；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果他是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不肖后代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他那白皙的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将永远捧着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民对你的指责！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我有一位"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当收购员的朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要是知道了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的“慷慨之举”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里该有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么难过——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他得知"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛耳朵里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有几根茸毛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能换取外汇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几年来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他辛勤地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剪呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟剪了十斤多……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象春蚕抽丝那般"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国积累财富，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有什么权利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把先烈的热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把人民对党的信赖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把劳动者辛勤的汗水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肆无忌惮地挥霍？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道周总理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄严宣告的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四个现代化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道党和人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍住十年伤痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在炉前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在田野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为之挥汗流血的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四个现代化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟是你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打着饱嗝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信手弹给我们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唾沫？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真不幸——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的将军！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一次长征"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你征服了大渡河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的长征，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你想过了没有——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你再后退一步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会变成了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渡——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河——！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛金星的悲剧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不会重演——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉默！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但愿我的诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也化作万钧雷霆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挟带着雄风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲进你的耳朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲进你的心窝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这新长征的路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且听前进的后人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和前进的法律一道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大喝一声："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“将军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样做！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1979，6，14，三稿于北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载《诗刊》一九七九年第八期）"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}